<h1>✏️ AI Pen Privacy Policy</h1>
<p><strong>Last updated: June 4, 2026</strong></p>

<h2>Data Collection</h2>
<p>AI Pen Expand<strong>不收集</strong>任何个人身份信息、浏览History或使用Data。我们重视您的隐私。</p>

<h2>API 使用</h2>
<p>您选中的文本会发送到 DeepSeek API 进行AI处理。API Key Storage在您本地的 Chrome Storage 中，仅用于调用 DeepSeek 接口。</p>
<p>Text content is discarded after DeepSeek API returns the result. We <strong>do not save, record, or upload</strong> any text content.</p>

<h2>Storage</h2>
<p>仅Storage以下Data在您本地浏览器：API Key、每日使用计数、最近的RewriteHistory记录。</p>

<h2>Permissions</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>activeTab</strong>：Read selected text on the current page</li>
<li><strong>storage</strong>：SaveSettings和使用记录</li>
<li><strong>host_permissions</strong>：Call the DeepSeek API</li>
</ul>

<h2>Contact Us</h2>
<p>tulv202900@163.com</p>
<footer><p>AI Pen © 2026</p></footer>
</body>
